                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "Older people must create alliances with other groups; otherwise, they have no bargaining power."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "Once social systems have been established for the good of all, including the elderly, they must not be altered or tampered with."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "Older people must accept their plight in life; otherwise, they will create disharmony for other groups."
                },
